### Backend Package dependencies Installation
python -m venv {name of environement} - Creates a Virtual Environment
pip install passlib[bcrypt] - Library for Hashing
pip install fastapi[all] - Framework for API development
pip install sqlalchemy - ORM for database Modles & Tables
pip install alembic - Migration tool for Database Models
pip install jinja - For fastapi rendering of Template


